    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What a steal! This old virtual pet game from the 90s was almost <strong>free</strong> at a yard sale two blocks away, and it was <i>just</i> the thing you were looking for!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now it's time to meet <strong>Babette</strong>, the cute cat that lives inside this bright little casing. Babette is dying to play with you! If you keep her happy, you might gain a friend for life! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140110/extras/a9083d5c724ad069d385c242016583bd.apng?t=1756213815\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140110/extras/a9083d5c724ad069d385c242016583bd.poster.avif?t=1756213815\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=118 /></picture></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more you take care of Babette, the more things seem <i>off</i>. Feeding her, playing with her, petting her... it becomes more and more difficult. She seems to be developing a mind of her own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You hear footsteps outside your house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Doors opening downstairs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eyes in the dark, staring at you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who is inside your house? And is this cute kitten trying to break free?  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140110/extras/3324364896a03cca9fc1b756885d540a.apng?t=1756213815\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140110/extras/3324364896a03cca9fc1b756885d540a.poster.avif?t=1756213815\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=118 /></picture></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the game, you will cuddle up in your bedroom and play through five levels, each more difficult than the last. Keep Babette happy by using the unique button combination of the pet egg to perform mini-games:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pet her!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feed her!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with her!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blood sacrifice!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play hide and seek!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do badly, and Babette will get mad. Balance keeping Babette happy with filling the progress bar to finish the level and make her go 'night night!'</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140110/extras/949df4e5526671f0435508226f9e023b.apng?t=1756213815\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140110/extras/949df4e5526671f0435508226f9e023b.poster.avif?t=1756213815\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=166 /></picture></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the events of the main game, you get vivid nightmares. It's like she's there, inside your head. The level begins, but this time it's different. So much more difficult. If you lose to Babette this time, you might lose it all...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you keep Babette happy? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you keep Babette contained?</p>",
